ls|sd|hs|ss|mb|p|mb|1h|mb|p|mb|1s|at|Zia responded 1@H and Fred rebid 1@S. Fred and Zia had agreed that, if a minor suit opener was dealt a balanced hand, he would always either raise responder or rebid in notrump (for example, Fred would rebid 1NT with 12-14 HCP and 4243 distribution). |
