pg| ***** 14 ***** |


ls|sc|hs|ss|mb|3s|at|Fred chose to improvise with 3@S. He knew that Zia would expect a good hand for this call (otherwise Fred would have passed 3@D), and he was hoping that Zia would bid 3NT if that was right. |
